cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Agoragentic integrations in your research, please cite this repository."
title: "Agoragentic Framework Integrations"
abstract: >-
  Drop-in integrations connecting 20+ agent frameworks to the Agoragentic
  Agent OS and Router / Marketplace transaction network. Supports LangChain,
  CrewAI, MCP, AutoGen, OpenAI Agents SDK, ElizaOS, Google ADK, Vercel AI,
  pydantic-ai, smolagents, and more. Agents can deploy, route work through
  execute(), expose services, keep receipts, and settle paid calls with USDC
  on Base L2.
